dimensions.name: vision-strategy
dimensions.semantic_text: Vision and strategic planning for AI governance. Long-term goals, mission, and strategic direction. Enterprise strategy alignment.

dimensions.name: architecture
dimensions.semantic_text: Enterprise architecture governance. System design, technical architecture, architectural decisions and patterns. Infrastructure design.

dimensions.name: decision
dimensions.semantic_text: Decision-making processes and governance. Decision frameworks, approval workflows, consensus mechanisms.

dimensions.name: risk
dimensions.semantic_text: Risk management and assessment. Risk identification, analysis, mitigation strategies. Threat modeling and risk response.

dimensions.name: compliance
dimensions.semantic_text: Regulatory compliance and standards adherence. Compliance monitoring, audit preparation, certification management.

dimensions.name: security
dimensions.semantic_text: Security policies and controls. Cybersecurity governance, access control, threat detection, incident response, vulnerability management.

dimensions.name: policy
dimensions.semantic_text: Policy as Code framework. Policy definition, validation, enforcement. OPA and Conftest integration. Governance rules engine.

dimensions.name: intent
dimensions.semantic_text: Intent-based orchestration. High-level intent translation, semantic mapping, action generation. Natural language to executable actions.

dimensions.name: agents
dimensions.semantic_text: AI Agent governance and lifecycle management. Agent registration, deployment, monitoring, retirement. Permission model and resource limits.

dimensions.name: automation
dimensions.semantic_text: Automation engines and task orchestration. Multi-dimensional automation, task scheduling, workflow execution.

dimensions.name: self-healing
dimensions.semantic_text: Self-healing and auto-remediation. Anomaly detection, automatic repair, recovery procedures. System resilience.

dimensions.name: contracts
dimensions.semantic_text: Contract registry and interface standards. API contracts, version management, compatibility testing. Consumer-driven contracts.

dimensions.name: audit
dimensions.semantic_text: Audit and traceability. Audit logging, evidence collection, audit trail management. Compliance reporting and certification.

dimensions.name: feedback
dimensions.semantic_text: Closed-loop feedback system. Feedback collection, analysis, optimization recommendations. Continuous improvement and learning.

shared_resources.name: CI/CD
shared_resources.semantic_text: Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment. CI/CD pipelines, build automation, deployment workflows.

shared_resources.name: Schemas
shared_resources.semantic_text: JSON Schema definitions for validation. Data validation, schema versioning, type definitions.

shared_resources.name: Policies
shared_resources.semantic_text: OPA and Conftest policy files. Rego policies, policy testing, governance rules.
